# Add Two Numbers -- Fourmilab AE card deck
#
# Computes: 3 + 5 = 8
# N000 loads 3 into column 0, N001 loads 5 into column 1.
# L000 loads column 0 into the result register.
# L001 loads column 1 into the prior register.
# + adds prior and result.
# P prints the result (should output 8).
# H halts.

N000 +3
N001 +5
L000
L001
+
P
H
